Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在測驗中請當心不要睡著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也不準
